rComments: Great prof! Really kind and lectures and interesting.

Constance George is not a psychologist, she's an elementary school guidance counselor with MA. She expresses that women are more verbal than men yet, she was very repetitive and read the power points word for word "verbatim"- When her mic turns off she starts stuttering and claims she's recording her lectures and goes on tangents.

Hands down best prof I've had! A truly inspirational teacher, loves what she does, uses real life examples from her own experiences (she's a psychologist). Class was a midterm, optional group presentation, final and attendance. Highly recommended!
